{script} {DARK}-t {GREEN}192{WHITE}.{GREEN}168{WHITE}.{GREEN}56{WHITE}.{GREEN}104 {DARK}-u {GREEN}admin {DARK}-w {GREEN}dictionary{WHITE}.{GREEN}txt
